data.description:
An Absolute Must See this Completely Renewed Home!  This Fantastic Pool Home has New Barrel Tiled Roof, New Wood Grain Luxury Laminate Flooring in the entire home. Freshly Interior Paint throughout. Updated Spacious Kitchen with New Cabinets and Quartz Counter Tops. New Upgraded Kitchen Appliances. Updated Bathroom Appointments including  New Walk in Showers, Vanities and Toilets. New Sheer Zebra Blinds. Storm Shutters and Oversized Garage with roll down screen.
This home has an incredible view of Pool, Golf Course and Lake from most rooms.
Be the first to enjoy all the new amenities!
